{"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent011RadioButtonB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships"}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider\/sizes"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider\/RadioButtonComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for radio button component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the radio button component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMinWidth: SizeSemanticToken { sizes.iconWithLabelLargeSizeXl }","","        override var borderWidthSelected: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThin }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider: RadioButtonComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(radioButton: CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(radioButton: CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    let radioButtonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, border, color and opacity semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let radioButtonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider()))"]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of radio button"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for  "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radios"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButtonItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RadioButtonComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","tex